    <item>
      <title>销售前景疲弱，塔塔汽车股价跌幅两年来最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/jaguar-owner-tata-motors-shares-sink-on-weak-sales-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拥有豪华SUV品牌捷豹路虎的印度汽车制造商塔塔汽车有限公司(Tata Motors Ltd.)的股价在该公司表示对销售前景持谨慎态度后，股价出现两年多以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/jaguar-owner-tata-motors-shares-sink-on-weak-sales-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 04:24:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
